\id 1PE - Zyphe
\h 1 PITER
\toc1 PITER CAKUA UIKHEHNAH
\toc2 1 PITER
\toc3 1 Pit
\mt1 PITER
\mt2 CAKUA UIKHEHNAH
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Zisu Khri apostol a cangpaw kama Piter tah Khazing tah a thingpaw khazaw letei khuachai a cangpaw, Pontas le Kalati le Kapadosia le Asia le Bithinia raang chung letah a paipatlawpaw sahlo letah ca ka ca kua he.
\v 2 Kaa Paw a cangpaw Khazing a hnihlangnah hratah thingpaw cang he ceh ka, Thlawpaw Pathai tah pathai sahpaw na cang he ceh. Ma pawco Zisu Khri a bia khah nge he ceh ka, a thisai tah sipathai na cang he ceh.
\p Ningdonah le thlawlungnah cawh a hluihlung tah naa tei cang ky seh.
\s1 Ahringpaw hnabeisuinah cawtah Khazing reithai
\p 
\v 3 Khazing le kaa Buipaw Zisu Khri a Paw cawh reithai tah ung ky seh! A zawngenah alai tu cawtah Zisu Khri thihnah taitah a thokawnah thongtah pithanah khah hnabeisuinah ahringpaw chung letah a ma peh.
\v 4 Ama taco a rawh khy lypaw, a thu thai lypaw, a ling thai lypaw, vaicung letah naaning naa cawtah ry cy ruapaw a ca chiapah he.
\v 5 Cai hningcai letei palang rua pawtah pachia ciapaw pachahnah cai a va chuanah tai zingnah thongtah Khazing hmingtuakhyná tah a ca vai he.
\v 6 Macawtaco, atoheh cai cuitei cawh hnehsahnah a phingphing chung letah ngechianah naa ing naná teitah a lawng ngetei my lo.
\v 7 Ma hming sahlo naa cung letei a tlungpaw heh naa zingnah a patahzia a lang nápaw cawtah a cang. Ma zingnah cawh me tah pathaisah ciapaw a cang naná teitah a rawh khypaw sui navy tah amai a hlu vypaw a cang. Ma hming sahlo cawh Zisu Khri a va lang tihtah reithainah, rungnawnah le hmezawnah peh naa cang nápaw a cang.
\v 8 Ama cawh naa hmuh bang ly naná teitah naa do, ato lehei zong naa hmuh ly naná teitah Ama cawh zing he ceh ka, hmokaw tei rei khy lypaw a rungnawpaw alawngnah khatah na chih he ceh.
\v 9 Zecawtamaw tatah naa zingnah tei a tingpaw naa thlawpaw pachahnah khah naa hmuh leimei.
\p 
\v 10 Ma pachahnah kong khatah a peitle tah Khazing khuavang sahlo tah aa reipaw, naaning khatah a va chuh lepaw ningdonah cawh hni pase du tah a raering ngeteipaw tah aa hui caimangpaw cang ka,
\v 11 aaning letei a ungpaw Khri Thlawpaw tah Khri a tai-ingnah vytei leh a va pazuipaw rungnawnah a rei hlang tihtah a so dupaw cai le ning le a konglang khah hni aa zong he.
\v 12 Khazing khuavang sahlo tei aa za hrepaw rai khah aaning aa cawtah cang lytah naaning naa cawtah a cang hri takhah aaning khatah a langsah. Vaicung taitei za thlawpaw Thlawpaw Pathai bawnah thongtah thawngchawbia a reitu sahlo tah aa ca ching he. Ma hming sahlo heh vaiming sahlo tahmai hmuh aa du ngeteipaw khah a cang.
\s1 Pathai my lo
\p 
\v 13 Macawtaco raihre rua pawtah naa thinglung cawh a pachia la, ma leh pung a uh khypaw cang my lo; Zisu Khri a lang tihtah naa hmuh ruapaw ningdonah lekhei na hnabeisuinah khah chia thlang my lo.
\v 14 Rei a ngepaw sawtei hratah ung la, zehmai naa hni ly ningcai tei naa pungsaw duná tah naa za ungpaw hrakhei ung khawh khé lo.
\v 15 Canghrasala, naaning a ca ytupaw he a pathaipaw hratah naaning zong naa tuapaw maikaw lekhei pathai my seh lo.
\v 16 Zecawtamaw tatah Khazing tah Capathai letah, “Kama ka pathaipaw hratah naaning zong pathai my lo,”\x + \xo 1:16 \xt Tlangbui 11:44-45; 19:2; 20:7\x* tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 17 Cawngsaw vytei patlia ly tei rai aa hrepaw naning teitah bia a pacepaw cawh Paw tatei naa ypaw khah a cangnah cawtah ma aluicung lehei khuachai sahlo hratah naa ung chung tahei Ama cizaw hmo teitah ung my lo.
\v 18 Naa mapaw sahlo tei aa ca rypaw he a chahnai lypaw hringzia taitei a ca pachah pawhe cawh a rawh thaipaw sui le ngung hapaw cang be,
\v 19 canghrasala, reipachianah le tling lynah a hnui lypaw Tuu teitei Khri thisai sung tah tlangpaw na cang he ceh.
\v 20 Ama cawh khazaw tua a cang hlai tah thing ciapaw cang ka, canghrasala ma caichangnah lehei naa cawtah palang a cang.
\v 21 Ama khah thihnah taitah patho kaw ka, rungnawnah a peipaw Khazing khah Ama a thongtah zing he ceh ka, macawtaco naa hnabeisuinah le naa zingnah cawh Khazing letah a ung.
\p 
\v 22 Atoheh cawh biahmuisui reingenah thongtah naaning le naaning cawh a pathaisah thah he ceh ka, macawtaco naa uny a cangpaw he khatah donah hmuisui naa hnuipaw a cang. Pakheh le pakheh naa lungthing hmuisui tah a do my lo.
\v 23 Ahringpaw le a hming pariapaw Khazing bia thongtah a rawh khypaw thleci taitah cang lytah a rawh khy lypaw thleci taitah naa pitha thah he ceh.
\v 24 Zecawtamaw tatah,
\q1 “Ming vytei cawh araang hratah cang he ka,
\q2 aa rungnawnah zong cawh ly letei pangpa sahlo hratah a cang he.
\q1 Araang cawh caa ka, pangpa sahlo cawh aa ling he.
\q2 
\v 25 Canghrasala, Abuipaw a bia cawh a hming paria thlang,”\x + \xo 1:25 \xt Isai 40:6-8\x*
\m tahpaw hratah. Taico, ma heh naaning khatei za reipaw thawngchawbia khah a cang hi.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Macawtaco ziahnuinah vytei le hinghenah vytei le, cungmai raipha cangnah le, hnachuanah le conguinah vytei khah naaning taitah vathlang my lo.
\v 2 A chuh thapaw hasaitei hratah thlawpaw lang meimeitui a pathaipaw khah a sah pui tah tlechai my lo, ma hraco naa tua caco pachahnah letah naa changchy he ceh.
\v 3 Zecawtamaw tatah Abuipaw cawh a chah takhah naa pateh thah myca cawtah.
\s1 Hringnah lungpui le thingpaw mingphing
\p 
\v 4 Ahringpaw alung, cawngsaw tah hlawhpaw, canghrasala Khazing tah a thingpaw le Ama a cawtah a sungpaw Zisu khatah aa vongpaw na cang he ceh.
\v 5 Naaning sahlo zong ahringpaw alung hratah thlawpaw lang ing tah sahpaw na cang he ceh. A pathaipaw tlangbui phu a cang ruapaw cang he ceh ka, Zisu Khri thongtah Khazing lung a tongpaw thlawpaw lang thuihlainah a tuapaw na cang he ceh.
\v 6 Zecawtamaw tatah Capathai letah,
\q1 “Mingtua hmai! Zion khuapui letah alung khah ka chia,
\q2 ma alung cawh thingpaw le a mai a sungpaw ingki lung a cang,
\q1 Ama aa zingpaw maikaw cawh
\q2 zening tahmai ningzaw tah ung by bei he,”\x + \xo 2:6 \xt Isai 28:16\x*
\m a tah.
\v 7 Ma cawh a zingpaw naaning naa caw taco a sungpaw alung a cang. Canghrasala a zing lypaw sahlo caw taco,
\q1 “Ing a sahtu sahlo tei aa hlawh ciapaw alung cawh
\q2 ingki letah abiapui caipaw tah a va cang,”\x + \xo 2:7 \xt Hlaw 118:22\x*
\m 
\v 8 mataico,
\q1 “Ma alung taco cawngsaw khah a pachihlysah he ka,
\q2 a pohlysah he.”\x + \xo 2:8 \xt Isai 8:14\x*
\m tatah Capathai tah a tah. A pachihly pawhe cawh thawngchawbia khah aa nge lynah cawtah cang ka, ma cawh aa cawtah khykhi ciapaw khah a cang.
\p 
\v 9 Canghrasala naaning cawh thingpaw cawngsaw, abui tlangbui phu, a pathaipaw mingphing, Khazing a cawngsaw na cang he ceh. Ma cawh muinah chung taitah khuarawha a chuipaw khainah lang a ca hruichuatu pawhe naa reithai khy nápaw cawtah a cang.
\v 10 Khuahlai taco naaning cawh ze cawngsaw hmai za cang bei he ceh, canghrasala atoheh cawh Khazing cawngsaw na cang myca he ceh. Khuahlai taco zaangsawnah khah za ting bang bei he ceh, canghrasala atoheh cawh Khazing zaangsawnah khah naa ting myca.
\p 
\v 11 Dopaw vesaw sahlo, ma khazaw lehei mehtha le khuachai hratah cang he ceh ka, macawtaco naa thlawpaw carae a cangpaw sua dunah khah cahri my lo tahpaw heh ka ca sia he.
\v 12 Lawki cawngsaw sahlo hrong lekhei hringzia achawpaw khei hring la, hmingchahly a tuapaw tatah aa ca tah hmai he tah hmingchaw naa tuapaw khah hmuh a he ka, Khazing tah bia a pace ning taco Khazing khah aa reithai a.
\s1 Uhtu le bui a cangpaw khatah a pehnah
\p 
\v 13 Abuipaw rawng tah cawngsaw hrong letah padawpaw nawhnuinah maikaw bia khah nge my lo. A sang caipaw nawhnuinah a hnuipaw abui a cang zong tah,
\v 14 hmingsua a tuapaw dangtah rua pawtah le hmingchaw a tuapaw mingchahnah peh rua pawtah abui tah tawpaw uhtubui a cang zong tah aa rei nge my lo.
\v 15 Khazing dunah cawh, zehmai hni ly tei naa kongchia a reipaw sahlo he khah hmingchaw naa tuasaná khei de ky tah tua khah a cang.
\v 16 Zalong teitah ung la, canghrasala naa zalongnah cawh hmingsua bakhunah takhei hmang khe lo. Khazing sae sahlo hrakhei ung my lo.
\v 17 Cawngsaw maikaw khah a ningcang teitah hmezaw he la, zingtu uny sahlo khah do my lo, Khazing khah cizaw la, siangpahrang khah upah my lo.
\p 
\v 18 Sae sahlo, naa bui leh khah upahnah vytei khakhei aa rei nge la, mehchaw le zawngrawhnah a hnuipaw sahlo letah long cang lytah mehpiathy sahlo zong khah aa rei nge my lo.
\v 19 Cawngsaw pakheh tah Khazing a thuithlangnah cawtah a dih lypaw taithuinah khah a ing khy caco, ama cawh pachaw tlang a cang.
\v 20 Canghrasala hmingsua naa tuanah rawng tei tuh naa cangpaw le naa ingpaw cawh zemaw naa cawtah chahnainah a ung a? Canghrasala achawpaw naa tuapaw rawng tah taithuinah naa ing caco, Khazing mehmuh letah pachaw tlang a cang.
\v 21 Ma cawtah hei y naa cangpaw a cang, zecawtamaw tatah Khri cawh naa cawtah taithui ka, a mingpai ruapaw a ca chiapah sipaw he cawh a phehnei zui khah a cang.
\q1 
\v 22 “Ama cawh ze suanah hmai tua be ca ka,
\q2 a hmokaw taitah hingbia pia bang be.”\x + \xo 2:22 \xt Isai 53:9\x*
\m 
\v 23 Ze rei lytah aa pasipasa tihtah palei bei he, a taithui tih zong tah pachihnah bia rei be. Ma navy co, dingná tah bia a cetupaw, Khazing lekhei a pahnia hri.
\v 24 Ama hrahring tah a pung tah kaa suanah khah khraws cung letah pho ka, macawtaco suanah letah thi he peh ka, dingnah letah ka hring he peh. Aa tuhnahpaw a hmaw tah a ca dangsah thah he.
\v 25 Langpui a pavepaw tuu hratah cang hrah hmai la, atoheh cawh Tuukingtu le naa thlawpaw a Mingkaitu khatah na va paleh kaw thah he ceh.
\c 3
\s1 Nupui le pasae kong
\p 
\v 1 Ma hraco naaning nupui sahlo, naa pasae leh khah aa rai a daw la, ma hratei naa tua caco, Khazing bia a zingtu a cang lypaw pasae zong tah nupui leh hringzia taikhei bia rei hy lytah,
\v 2 naa hringzia a pathaipaw le hmezaw a tlahpaw khah aa hmuh tihtah Khazing bia cawh aa zing a.
\v 3 Naa hmuichahnah cawh alailang tei a pasangnah a cangpaw, sang a phia le sui le ngung a tua le chaichi chaw a tuaná khei cangsah khe lo.
\v 4 Ma navy co, hmuichahnah cawh naa chung taitah a ka chuapaw a cang. Ma hmuichahnah cawh Khazing mehmuh letah mai a hnui ngeteipaw, aningnaipaw le denah a dupaw lungthing, a ling thai lypaw khah a cangpaw a cang.
\v 5 Zecawtamaw tatah, khuahlai canu mehpathai sahlo, Khazing letei aa hnabeisuinah a pahniapaw he taco, ma hraco aa hmui chahnah khah aa za tua tei. Aaning leh aa pasae cacy khah aa rai a daw he ka,
\v 6 Sarah tah a pasae Abraham a bia khah nge katei, ka buipaw tatah a ypaw hratah aa cang. Hmingchaw naa tua caco le zehmai ci lytah naa ung caco, Sarah a sawcanu leh na cang he ceh.
\p 
\v 7 Ma hraco naaning pasae sahlo, naa nupui leh aa zawng raw la, pasungpanaw hmotah mingkai my lo; zecawtamaw tatah a thawdia vypaw a cangnah cawtah le Khazing tah a ca peh pawhe lahsong sung hringnah aa tinghruipaw naa cangnah cawtah. Ma hratei naa tua caco, naa thlawchangnah a ca pakhangpaw he zehmai ung be.
\s1 Hmingchaw tua rawng tah tai-ingnah
\p 
\v 8 A changnah letah ka ca ching dupaw he cawh, naa dawngkasawny tah lungthing hmokheh teitah ung la, naa zawng a rawh la, uny hratah pakheh le pakheh a do la, zawngrawhnah le rai a dawnah khatah ung my lo.
\v 9 Chahlynah khah chah ly ná tah palei khe la, zawngtenah khah zawngtenah tah paleh khe o, canghrasala bonghnang song hri la, zecawtamaw tatah ma cawpaw tahei y cang he ceh ka, bonghnang naa ting a.
\v 10 Capathai letah,
\q1 “Hringnah a pasung a panawpaw le
\q2 caichaw ningchaw hmuh a dupaw taco
\q1 bia chia reinah taikhei a lui a vai seh la,
\q2 a kaw tah hingbia rei kheh seh.
\q1 
\v 11 Chahlynah khah a huisai seh la, chahnah khah tua seh la,
\q2 denah khah hui seh la, a cadai seh.
\q1 
\v 12 Zecawtamaw tatah Abuipaw a meh cawh mehding sahlo cung letah ung ka,
\q2 aa thlawchangnah khah a nge pah du he,
\q1 canghrasala Abuipaw cawh chahlynah a tuapaw sahlo khah a carae he,”\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Hlaw 34:12-16\x*
\m tahpaw hratah.
\p 
\v 13 Hmingchaw tua a dupaw naa cang thlang pawtah a ca saw sápaw ahomaw a ung he a?
\v 14 Canghrasala, a dingpaw hming rawng tah naa tai-ing caco, bonghnang naa ting. “Aa cipaw khah ci khe lo, raechia tah ung khe lo.”\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Isai 8:12\x*
\v 15 Canghrasala naa lungthing chung letah Khri cawh Abuipaw tah tua my lo. Hnabeisuinah naa hnuipaw kong letah a silang a ca haepaw aa ung tihtah ching khy rua pawtah a maipacia tah ung paria thlang my lo. Canghrasala, ma hratei naa tua tih taco bianai teitah le hmezawnah chitah tua la,
\v 16 naa chiachaw thluidangnah lungthing a pathaipaw khah a tle paria thlang la, ma pawsui co, Khri letei naa ziaza a chawpaw a ca cawnguipaw sahlo cawh pachiapahrunah bia aa reipaw cung lekhei aa ning a zeh tae a.
\v 17 Chahlynah tua rawng tah taithuinah ing navy co, Khazing nawtlahnah a cang caco, chahnah tua rawng tah taithuinah ing cawh a chah vy.
\v 18 Zecawtamaw tatah Khri cawh kaa suanah cawtah uikheh tah a zaw pawtah thi ka, naaning khah Khazing lang seikhui pawtah mehdingpaw cawh mehding lypaw cawtah a thi. Pungsaw tah thihnah ing ka, canghrasala Thlawpaw tah a hringsah.
\v 19 Ma thong co, thong letah thlahpaw thlawpaw sahlo khakhei va sei ka, phung a rei.
\v 20 Ma thlawpaw sahlo cawh khuahlai Noah tah tuilawng a tuh chung vytei lungsy teitah Khazing tah a haw thlangning he takhei Khazing bia a za nge lypaw sahlo khah a cang he. Tuilawng chung letei mehnung cawngtei, mehnung pareh suipaw khah tui taitah pachah cang he ka,
\v 21 ma cawh atotei naaning a ca pachah pawhe, tui tei baptisma cangnah a hmuisang khah a cang. Baptisma cangnah cawh pungsaw taitah a pialuipaw lahpahnah cang be, Khazing lang letah chiachaw thluidangnah lungthing pathai tei biakangnah tuapaw a cang. Zisu Khri thihnah taitah a thokawnah tah a ca pachah he.
\v 22 Ama cawh vaicung lang ke ka, Khazing cacang lang letah a ty ka, vaiming vytei le nawhnuinah vytei le hmingtuakhynah vytei cawh a rai letah chia a cang he.
\c 4
\s1 Khazing cawtah hring
\p 
\v 1 Macawtaco, Khri zong tah a pungsaw tah a tai-ingpaw hrakhei, naaning zong ma hapaw tai-ingnah khakhei a pachia my lo, zecawtamaw tatah ma hratei taithuinah a ingpaw cawh suanah chung lekhei ung beh.
\v 2 A hringchung vytei pungsaw sua dunah cawtah cang lytah Khazing dunah hratah a hring hri tahnah a cang.
\v 3 Lawki cawngsaw sahlo tei tua pawtah aa thingpaw he ziaza a chiahrupaw hohenah, zuruinah, zucheinah hming letah a nawngsenah, langsianah, pasihpadawh a chuipaw nono behnah sahlo lekhei cai sypui naa za hmang thah hrah kho.
\v 4 Chahlynah aa tuapaw sahlo hrong letah naa tae khawh ly tih he ceh tah naa huivesaw paring sahlo cawh aa khuarawha ngetei ka, naa kongchia aa ca rei he.
\v 5 Canghrasala mehring kha mehthi kha biacepah pawtah a mai paciapaw Khazing hme letah aa kong cawh aa rei ceingei a.
\v 6 Macawtaco, a thi ciapaw sahlo khakhei zong thawngchawbia khah reipaw cang ka, ma pawsui co aaning cawh aa pungsaw khah aa tuasenah hratah biacepah aa cang khy taitah aa thlawpaw cawh Khazing khatah a hring khypaw a cang.
\p 
\v 7 Hming vytei a changnah ning cawh a ne myca. Macawtaco thlaw naa chang khy nápawtah naa lungthing pavang seh la, ma le ma a hraipaking khypaw cang my lo.
\v 8 Zezong navy tah pakheh le pakheh lung hmuisui tah a do la, zecawtamaw tatah donah taco suanah a hlupui khah a ngethai sah.
\v 9 Phingze lytah pakheh le pakheh a tlungke my lo.
\v 10 Pakheh cy tah aa hmuhpaw lahsong maikaw khah ming hringpaw bong nápawtah hmang he seh la, Khazing ningdonah khah zingchui teitah a phingphing tah hmang my lo.
\v 11 Pakheh kheh tah bia a rei caco, Khazing bia tei a reipaw hratah rei seh. Pakheh kheh tah a rai a hre caco, Khazing tah thawzaang a pehpaw hratah hre seh la, maco Zisu Khri thongtah Khazing khah zezongpui letah reithai a cang a. Laisuinah le hmingtuakhynah cawh chaizaw tah chaizaw tai Ama khatah ung ky seh. Amen!
\s1 Khrisaw cang rawng tah tai-ingnah
\p 
\v 12 Ka dopaw huivesaw sahlo, a sahpaw pasenah alaipui tah naa ing rawng takhei naa khuarawha kheh seh la, a ung bang lypaw hming sahlo zong naa cung letah a tlung leimei tatah zong pacang khe lo.
\v 13 Khri a tai-ingnah lekhei naa tai-ing hrahnah cawtah khei a lawng hri my lo, ma pawsui co a rungnawnah khatah a lang tihtah naa lunglawngnah a laihlui a.
\v 14 Khri a ming rawng tah zongte naa cang caco, bonghnang song na cang he ceh, zecawtamaw tatah rungnawnah Thlawpaw, Khazing Thlawpaw cawh naaning khatah a ung.
\v 15 Naa tai-ing caco, lenongpaw le aa rupaw le chahlynah a phingphing a tuapaw le male kong letah a cahro a catipaw hratah cang khe lo.
\v 16 Canghrasala Khrisaw naa cangnah rawng tah naa tai-ing caco, naa ningzeh kheh seh, Khri a ming khah naa kai cawtah Khazing khah reithai hri my lo.
\v 17 Zecawtamaw tatah atoheh Khazing biacenah cai cawh cang ka, Khazing ingchungkho taitah patho cang ka, kaaning taitah pathopaw a cang caco, Khazing thawngchawbia a nge lypaw sahlo aa cawtah zemaw aa chuh sialia a?
\v 18 Mataico Capathai tah,
\q1 “Mehding caw tahmai pachahnah hmuh a ru caco,
\q2 Khazing zetahmai a rei lypaw sahlo le mehsua sahlo cawh zekhatamaw aa cang tae a?”\x + \xo 4:18 \xt Biasing 11:31\x*
\m a tah.
\p 
\v 19 Macawtaco Khazing dunah hratah a tai-ingpaw sahlo taco, zingchuipaw aaning a Tuatu he khakhei a pei he seh la, hmingchaw khah tua lo leimei he seh.
\c 5
\s1 Macang sahlo le mehny sahlo khatah
\p 
\v 1 Naaning hrong letei khrisaw macang sahlo, naa raihre hui macang ka cangnah cawtah le Khri a tai-ingnah a hnikhuitu pakheh ka cang hlui tah a va lang lepaw rungnawnah zong a hrongpaw ka cangnah cawtah ka ca naw he.
\v 2 Naaning mingkainah rai letei chiapaw Khazing tuurung tuukingtu cang la, hringhrang tah cang lytah Khazing tah a ca dukhuipaw he hratah naaning lungtho teitah cang seh la, tangka letah duhlui hnui lytah rai hrepah a dupaw le,
\v 3 naaning tah mingkaipaw tei pehpaw sahlo cung letah abui hratah cang lytah tuurung sahlo cawtah a mingpai rua pawtah cang my lo.
\v 4 Mataico, Tuukingtu alaicaipaw a vong tihtah zening tahmai tah a ling khy lypaw rungnawnah builukhu khah naa cy tae a.
\p 
\v 5 Ma hraco mehny sahlo zong macang vypaw sahlo aa rai khah a daw my lo. Naa zongmingtei tah pakheh le pakheh cung letah a pany my lo, zecawtamaw tatah,
\q1 “Khazing tah a palaipaw cawh dy ka,
\q2 canghrasala a panypaw cawh ning a do.”\x + \xo 5:5 \xt Biasing 3:34\x*
\m 
\v 6 Macawtaco Khazing kih thawtlungnah rai letah naaning teitah a pany la, Ama tah a cai a zaw tihtah a ca cuicaling tae he a.
\v 7 Naaning naa zawng a rawh tupaw a cangnah cawtah naa lung reithuinah vytei khah Ama khah pei my lo.
\p 
\v 8 Ma le ma teitah a hraipaking khypaw cang la, a raering teitah ung my lo. Na caraepaw Setan cawh cakebarung hratah a ty khypaw cawngsaw ty rua pawtah a khiakaly leimei.
\v 9 Ma cawh dy tah zingnah letah cyky tah a daw la, zecawtamaw tatah khazaw raang ting letei a ungpaw naa uny sahlo cawh ma hapaw tai-ingnah sahlo khah aa ing hrah tahpaw khah naa hni thlang.
\p 
\v 10 Taico, cai cuitei chung naa tai-ing khy taitah Khri letei a chaizaw rungnawnah lang a ca hruitupaw he ningdonah vytei a hnuipaw, Khazing taco tlangtlingnah le thawzaang chongnah le a cypaw thahrang a ca pae he a.
\v 11 Hmingtuakhynah vytei cawh chaizaw tah chaizaw tai Ama a tei a cang. Amen.
\s1 Ahning cai kihtlenah
\p 
\v 12 Zing a chuipaw uny hratah ka rawhpaw Sailas tah a pa bawnah thongtah ma ca cuitei heh naaning khatah ca kua he neh ka, Khazing ningdonah hmuisui a cang tahpaw heh ka rei dupaw le ka ca pasy dupaw he a cang. Ma leco cyky tah a daw thlang my lo.
\p 
\v 13 Babilon khuapui letei a ungpaw, canuno,\f + \fr 5:13 \ft Canuno heh, \fq Khrisawbu,\ft tahnah a cang.\f* naaning khatei thing hrui a cangpaw takhei a dang pawtah ca tah he ka, ka sawcapaw Marka zong tah a dang pawtah a ca tah hrah he.
\v 14 Pakheh le pakheh khah donah hmuisui tah kih a tle my lo.
\p Zisu Khri chung letei a ungpaw vytei naa cung letah denah ung ky seh.
